data.description: Absolutely stunning! This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home in the sought-after Brookstone Subdivision is a true gem. From the moment you lay eyes on it, the great curb appeal with its covered front entry sets the tone for what lies inside. Step through the front door into the welcoming foyer and you'll find a versatile space that can be used as a dining room, front living room, or convenient home office. The thoughtful layout flows seamlessly into an open living room with gas fireplace that adjoins the spacious eat-in kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting sleek dark cabinets, elegant granite countertops, custom light fixtures, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The laundry room is fully equipped with shelving, built-in drop zone and spacious walk-in pantry. The spacious main floor master's en suite is a true retreat. Relax in the tiled rain shower or unwind in the spa tub, and then follow the path to a generous walk-in closet that offers plenty of storage space. Upstairs, you'll discover even more to love. A generous landing offers endless possibilities - from a playroom to a home gym or media room. Three additional large bedrooms grace the upper level, each featuring spacious closets to keep your living space organized. These bedrooms share a well-appointed full bathroom, making mornings a breeze for the whole family. Step outside, and you'll find an inviting backyard that's perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. The open space provides endless opportunities for landscaping and gardening, while a fantastic Trex deck beckons for outdoor entertaining and BBQs. The upper deck comes suited with concrete pad underneath and wiring for a hot tub. With possession at closing, this home is ready for you to move right in and start creating memories.
